title: E. Power Biggs plays Scott Joplin on the pedal harpsichord VINYL
description:
E. Power Biggs (he refuses to give his first name on the record sleeve) Plays Scott Joplin on the pedal harpsichord, 1973. Ripped from Vinyl LP@256Kbps. Definitely need to be in a (18)90s saloon mood for this one.
